{"key":"post-11258799","value":"<?xml version=\"1.0\"?>\n<post>\n<id>11258799</id>\n<content>Two things.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;Set the jars on a table to photograph.&amp;nbsp; Don't hold them in your hand, which is never still, thus blurring the picture.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;Turn off the flash.&amp;nbsp; All it does is cause a glare on the glass.&amp;nbsp; Set up two lights at a 45 degree angle to the jar so the glare points away from the camera.&amp;nbsp; This will result in an in-focus, non-glare picture as shown below.&lt;br /&gt;RR&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://files.shroomery.org/files/07-10/329565823-colonizing_brf_jars_004a.jpg&quot; class=&quot;highslide&quot; onclick=&quot;return hs.expand(this,{slideshowGroup:'hsg1'})&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;&lt;img style=&quot;max-width:192px;height:auto;&quot; src=&quot;/forums/thumbs/07-10/329565823-thumb_colonizing_brf_jars_004a.jpg&quot;&gt;&lt;/a&gt; &lt;a href=&quot;https://files.shroomery.org/files/07-009/255718132-jar_contaminants_001a.jpg&quot; class=&quot;highslide&quot; onclick=&quot;return hs.expand(this,{slideshowGroup:'hsg1'})&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;&lt;img style=&quot;max-width:192px;height:auto;&quot; src=&quot;/forums/thumbs/07-009/255718132-thumb_jar_contaminants_001a.jpg&quot;&gt;&lt;/a&gt; &lt;a href=&quot;https://files.shroomery.org/files/06-17/627178716-Rye_jar_ready_to_shake.jpg&quot; class=&quot;highslide&quot; onclick=&quot;return hs.expand(this,{slideshowGroup:'hsg1'})&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;&lt;img style=&quot;max-width:192px;height:auto;&quot; src=&quot;/forums/thumbs/06-17/627178716-thumb_Rye_jar_ready_to_shake.jpg&quot;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;</content>\n<name>RogerRabbit</name>\n<next>11258825</next>\n<prev>11258798</prev>\n<first>11258776</first>\n<last>11259459</last>\n<when>1255708227</when>\n<utime>10/16/09 06:50 PM</utime>\n</post>"}